item.title: This specific Router Portfowarding
item.dc:creator: @Illadelph Illadelph
item.description:
@Illadelph wrote:

Starting port:43594 (usually)
ending port:43594

Protocol:Both (if there isnt that option i think its TCP)
Lan ip address: go to ur cmd- type ipconfig, get your static ip and put it there.

and done… im pre sure i dont have this portforwarding. but it should be good or itleast really close.
